posting_body: ['Welcome home to Town Centre!', 'Located at:', '3475 Golfview Dr', 'Eagan, MN 55123', 'Rental Information:', '# of Bedrooms: 3', '# of Bathrooms:  2', 'Square Footage: 1231 sq ft', 'Rental Pricing: $2000/month', 'Contact our leasing office at', 'show contact info', 'We are a pet-friendly community with a dog park nearby, as well as plenty of outdoor space including sand volleyball courts, a playground, and picnic facilities.', "As a resident of our community, you'll have full access to our fitness center and our indoor pool for the MN winters and outdoor swimming pools.", 'Our clubhouse is also available for private events for your Twin City friends and family.', 'Community Features:', '● Cardio Machines', '● Disposal Chutes', '● Elevator', '● Fitness Center', '● Free Weights', '● Picnic Area', '● Playground', '● Pool', '● Smoke-Free', '● Views', '● 24 Hour Availability', '● Barbecue/Grill Area', '● Controlled Access Building', '● Intercom/Call Box', '● Laundry Facilities/Laundry Room', '● Off-Street Parking', '● On-site Management', '● Planned Social Activities', '● Reservable Clubhouse', '● Volleyball Court', 'Unit Features:', '● Air Conditioning', '● Dining Room', '● Dishwasher', '● Ice Maker In Select Homes', '● Intercom/Call Box', '● Linen Closet', '● Microwave', '● Vaulted Ceiling In Select Homes', '● Views', '● Washer/Dryer Included', 'Office Hours:', 'Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'show contact info', 'Pet Policy:', 'Dogs and Cats Allowed:', 'Max 2 allowed, One time Fee $250.00, Rent $30.00, Deposit $250.00.', 'Breed Restrictions Apply.', 'Leasing Options:', 'Variable', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Management:', 'Weidner Apartment Homes, LLC', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'E930FCC8D8944A33']
